quran[17]{c,v,t}:
  86,1,“Ndikulumbilira ku mwamba ndi Nyenyezi imene imadza usiku
  86,2,“Chitakudziwitse nchiyani za Nyenyezi yodza usikuyo
  86,3,“Imeneyo ndi nyenyezi yowala kwambiri (mu mdima)
  86,4,“Ndithudi palibe mzimu uliwonse koma uli ndi msungi wake (amene akuuyang’anira ndikulemba zonse zochita zake)
  86,5,"“Aganizire munthu, kodi adalengedwa kuchokera kuchiyani"
  86,6,“Adalengedwa kuchokera ku madzi ofwamphuka
  86,7,“Amatuluka kuchokera pakati pa mafupa a msana (wa mwamuna) ndi chifuwa (cha mkazi)
  86,8,"“Ndithu Iye ndiwakutha, kumbwezeranso (ku moyo pa mbuyo pa imfa)"
  86,9,“Tsiku limene zobisika zonse zidzaonekera poyera
  86,10,“Munthu sadzakhala ndi mphamvu (tsiku limenelo zodzitetezera iye mwini) ndiponso sadzakhala ndi mtetezi
  86,11,“Ndikulumbiliranso mitambo yobweretsabweretsa mvula
  86,12,“Ndi nthaka imene imang’ambika (potulutsa m’mera)
  86,13,“Ndithudi iyi (Qur’an) ndi mawu olekanitsa (Haqq ndi Bâtwil - choona ndi chonama)
  86,14,“Imeneyi sinkhambakamwa
  86,15,“Ndithudi iwo akukonza chiwembu
  86,16,“Nanenso ndikuwakonzera chiwembu (champhamvu kwambiri chimene sangathe kuchipewa)
  86,17,"“Basi, apatse nthawi osakhulupirira apatse nthawi pang’ono, (aona posachedwa)"